shortDescription: Commander, this is an extremely time-sensitive mission and we're on a strict deadline, so I hope you can assist us. Our covert forces are poised to seize a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} facility where a large number of {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} civilians are being held prisoner. However, the facility is protected by a nearby military base, and as soon as we seize the prison, they'll move against it, and reduce those buildings to rubble before they let us extract those people. We'll be moving our own 'Mechs and Leopards in as quickly as we can but before we can land them and extract the civilians, we need you to pacify that military base.
longDescription: I'm guessing these 'civilians' are some kind of covert operatives, for this much metal to be put on the field to extract them.

dialogueContent.words: Argo, we've taken control of the facility. Our DropShips are on station; as soon as the area's secure we'll start evacuating our people.
Acknowledged. Meyer, how long have we got before the bad guys respond?
Uh, now? They're inbound to you now?
Commander, they're going to keep sending 'Mechs at us until they destroy this base. You'll need to get their attention or they'll bury the civilians in rubble.
The good news is that once you take out the military facility, they'll have no eyes on their LZ, so they'll have to stop landing more forces.
Darius, you have a really weird definition of 'good news'. Commander, I'll move in for a pickup once you get that base flattened. Don't keep me waiting.
We've got it from here, Argo. Thanks for the help.
Another job well done.
That could have gone better. Let's debrief back in orbit, Commander.
Commander, enemy turrets identified.
Commander, I'm seeing hostile defenders surrounding the enemy base.
We can't complete the contract until those units are destroyed.
Hey, boss, I hate to bring bad news, but I've got eyes on enemy units surrounding their base. Looks like you're gonna have to shoot your way through.
That's the first target structure down, Commander. Keep up the pressure.
Argo, our facility is taking fire over here. We need you to draw that fire off, or we're dead!
Argo, we've lost one of our structures. You've got to move faster, or we'll lose them all!
Argo, we're under heavy-- [static]-- hold out-- [static]
Dammit! Commander, we've only got one building left. If it goes down, I'm scrubbing the contract.
That's the last structure, Commander. That should slow down the attackers. Meyer, are you ready for pickup?
Affirmative, XO. Let's get out of here, boss.
Commander, we've completed all the primary objectives and you're clear to extract.
I'm on station to pick you up here whenever you're ready, boss.
As long as you're still in the AO, Commander, you'll need to keep the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} base secure.
Commander, that's all the enemy forces. There's a {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} lance ready to relieve you.
When you're ready to extract, Sumire will pick you up at this location.
Heads up, commander, a lance of {TEAM_HOST.FactionDef.Demonym} units just entered the area. They're hostile to everyone!
We'll have to destroy that lance if we want to complete the mission.
Heads up, commander, a lance of {TEAM_HOST.FactionDef.Demonym} units just entered the area. They're hostile to everyone!
If we destroy them we'll get a hefty bonus.
Commander, I'm seeing hostile {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Demonym} units in the area. Our target brought in allies for backup.
Our employer is saying we NEED to kill those units. Prepare to engage.
Commander, I'm seeing hostile {TEAM_TAR_ALLY.FactionDef.Demonym} units in the area. Our target brought in allies for backup.
If we decide to kill these units our employer if offering a bonus.
A lance of hostile {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} has landed nearby.
Our employer wants us to kill these guys. This mission isn't ending until they die.
A lance of hostile {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} has landed nearby.
Our employer is offering us some extra cash if we destroy these units too.
Scratch another target.
Good job, commander. All primary objectives complete. Get to evac, Sumire will pick you up here.
Commander, a {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} Leopard just dropped another lance into the AO.
They'll keep landing more units until you take out that base.
That's another {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} lance in the field. Getting kinda crowded down there.
Another enemy lance in the AO, Commander.
Commander, more hostiles are entering the area. I've marked their LZ.
Commander, more hostiles are entering the area. I've marked their LZ.
Commander, we've got an enemy lance moving towards the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} base.
Commander, we've got an enemy lance moving towards the {TEAM_EMP.FactionDef.Demonym} base.
Commander, {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} reinforcements are inbound to this location.
Commander, {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} reinforcements are inbound to this location.
Commander, {TEAM_TAR.FactionDef.Demonym} reinforcements are inbound to this location.
Argo, our forces are ready to assist in defending the base.
Acknowledged. Commander, they'll stay near the base and intercept any hostiles that make it past your lance.
Argo, we're falling back to our base to hold off the attackers. Good luck out there.
